{"title":"Video: Hand Building the BLUEPRINT Trail in BC, a Shimano Original","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/21/video-hand-building-the-blueprint-trail-in-bc-a-shimano-original/","date":1626859905000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span dir=\"auto\">Mark Matthews, Chris Snodgrass, James Walter, Scott Bell, Jarrett Lindal and Arne Newman. Who are they? The guys who put back breaking work into the creation of the new BLUEPRINT Flow Trail in Cumberland, BC. With the support of Shimano, the United Riders of Cumberland and Mosaic Forest Management, Mark Mathews tells the story of hand building a Blue Square Level flow trail from scratch, with some beautiful shots capturing the fresh trail “appearing”, as if from nowhere, as the rider sails through the air and rails new turns.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" alt=\"mattock hoe trail building tools blueprint flow trail bc\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" ezoid=\"0.5534371830093148\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052210/mattock-hoe-trail-building-tools-blueprint-flow-cumberland-bc-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com