reativity further than we had planned.</em></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada.jpg\" alt=\"shiamno blueorint trail building process\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21052406/shimano-blueprint-trail-building-british-columbia-canada-631x420.jpg 631w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" da